    "name": "Dungeon Shifters",
    "steam_appid": 3403100,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/e5ecc117fbe4fc6119d5cc96fe201709.poster.avif?t=1755692075\" width=598 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/e5ecc117fbe4fc6119d5cc96fe201709.webm?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/e5ecc117fbe4fc6119d5cc96fe201709.mp4?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explora las profundidades implacables...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forja tu camino a través de un mundo fracturado por un cometa mágico.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dungeon Shifters</strong> es un <i>RPG de acción</i> ambientado en el año 0 de una catástrofe mundial. Este juego te desafía a descubrir una magia oculta y sobrevivir a lo que se esconde bajo ella.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Características principales</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exploración profunda de mazmorras</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desciende a mazmorras repletas de caminos, pasajes bloqueados, habitaciones ocultas y artefactos antiguos. Descubre murales olvidados, fragmentos de historia y acertijos mientras reconstruyes un pasado oscuro.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/728327c22ce6d7faf04450aa120a7dfd.poster.avif?t=1755692075\" width=598 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/728327c22ce6d7faf04450aa120a7dfd.webm?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/728327c22ce6d7faf04450aa120a7dfd.mp4?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combate en tercera persona</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enfréntate a enemigos en un sistema de combate estratégico y pausado. La gestión de la energía, la presición y la lectura de patrones enemigos son clave para sobrevivir.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/b45a633304d4cdb23334cd5808a6b465.poster.avif?t=1755692075\" width=598 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/b45a633304d4cdb23334cd5808a6b465.webm?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/b45a633304d4cdb23334cd5808a6b465.mp4?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/bc355f9c38180b2c445c63afb8fe10cd.poster.avif?t=1755692075\" width=598 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/bc355f9c38180b2c445c63afb8fe10cd.webm?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/bc355f9c38180b2c445c63afb8fe10cd.mp4?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tres clases jugables con estilos únicos</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cada una con su propio ritmo de combate, rol y preferencias de equipamiento:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Guerrero del Martillo</strong>: resistente, especializado en combate cuerpo a cuerpo y control de multitudes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Guerrero de Espada Larga</strong>: duelista ágil, ideal para enfrentamientos 1 a 1 y contraataques.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Maga del Agua</strong>: hechicera de largo alcance que manipula magia elemental en tiempo real.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/6fdc6c9a94556ad4074073abd360b0f4.poster.avif?t=1755692075\" width=598 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/6fdc6c9a94556ad4074073abd360b0f4.webm?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/6fdc6c9a94556ad4074073abd360b0f4.mp4?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enemigos con comportamientos distintos</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Portaescudos</strong>: bloquean ataques frontales y te obligan a reposicionarte.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Espadachines frenéticos</strong>: se lanzan desde lejos y castigan los errores de distancia.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arqueros Lamentosos</strong>: disparan flechas malditas que interrumpen a los hechiceros.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jefes únicos</strong> que pondrán a prueba todo lo que has aprendido. Cada encuentro exige que aprendas, te adaptes y domines el combate.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/5e322bc8db362124998fbf59bbda69a9.poster.avif?t=1755692075\" width=598 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/5e322bc8db362124998fbf59bbda69a9.webm?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/5e322bc8db362124998fbf59bbda69a9.mp4?t=1755692075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Narrativa ambiental en un mundo vivo</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El mundo de <i>Dungeon Shifters</i> es complejo y está lleno de secretos. Descubre su historia a través de escrituras olvidadas, murales y señales visuales ocultas en cada nivel. Cuanto más profundo desciendas, más clara se vuelve la verdad… si sobrevives para verla.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>¿Estás listo para descender?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cada camino que tomes, cada enemigo que enfrentes y cada secreto que descubras formará parte de tu historia. <strong>Descubre lo olvidado. Cambia el destino de tu mundo.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras/e8e3bff65c75b32c1771443619d9988c.avif?t=1755692075\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3403100/extras_big/e8e3bff65c75b32c1771443619d9988c.avif?t=1755692075 width=800 height=458 /></span></p>",
